550
00:31:10,510 --> 00:31:11,510
Ay, mi Manuel.

551
00:31:12,010 --> 00:31:13,010
Sí.

552
00:31:14,170 --> 00:31:15,170
¿De veras?

553
00:31:15,290 --> 00:31:16,290
Sí.

554
